title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Raymundo: PART 1
itunes:title: Best Bits with Morgan and Special Guest Raymundo: PART 1
description:
On this weekends part 1, you’ll hear Morgan and Raymundo share the things they’re obsessed with right now, and the current TV shows/movies they recommend. Morgan talked about a savage thing she did recently and some Food Worlds. Raymundo talked about the “Baecation Pt. 2” filming happening this weekend and he shared a life update. And of course they answered some random questions!

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
